casebody.data:
LIBERTARIANS FOR TRANSPARENT GOVERNMENT, a NJ Nonprofit Corporation, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
The OCEAN COUNTY PROSECUTOR'S OFFICE and John C. Tassini, in His Official Capacity as Records Custodian for the Ocean County Prosecutor's Office, Defendants-Respondents. C-868 September Term 2017
080706 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 21, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001608-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
